 need of dependence on </div><div class="t m11d x33 h21 y1eed ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God.&quot;—Prophets and Kings, </div><div class="t m86e xba he yc67 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page 30. </div><div class="t me40 x2e h2f y1b04 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 27 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
